name: Jelly Fish Crush
description:
Match cute jelly fish in this fun and challenging match-3 adventure!

MAIN FEATURES:
▲ 300+ addictive puzzles with more added all the time!
▲ Amazing arsenal of powerups & combos!
▲ Free & easy to play, challenging to master!
▲ Stunning graphics & adorable animations!

Jelly Fish Crush is free to download and play, but contains optional in-app purchases that cost real money.
publishers: Beijing New Vision Real Estate Development Co
